            4.3. Adding Records
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
https://www.xyzpub.com/en/ruby-on-rails/3.2/activerecord_datensaetze_hinzufuegen.html
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------
        WORKS WONDERS
---------------------------------
====================================================================================================
User.create!({:email => "guy@gmail.com", :password => "111111", :password_confirmation => "111111" })
====================================================================================================




            4.7. Editing a Record

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
